{"text_id":122476,"tokens":["In"," this"," work",","," we"," present"," a"," theoretical"," resolution"," of"," magnetic"," re","connection"," in"," high"," energy"," plas","mas","."," Our"," study"," focuses"," on"," understanding"," the"," underlying"," mechanisms"," that"," govern"," magnetic"," re","connection",","," which"," is"," one"," of"," the"," most"," fundamental"," phenomena"," in"," astro","physical"," and"," space"," plas","mas","."," To"," achieve"," this"," goal",","," we"," applied"," analytical"," and"," numerical"," methods"," based"," on"," the"," principles"," of"," plasma"," physics"," and"," magneto","hydro","dynamics"," (","M","HD",")."," We"," investigate"," the"," influence"," of"," magnetic"," fields"," on"," particle"," transport",","," energy"," dissipation",","," and"," plasma"," dynamics","."," Our"," study"," revealed"," that"," current"," sheet"," thinning"," and"," instability"," in"," plas","mas"," are"," the"," key"," factors"," that"," trigger"," magnetic"," re","connection","."," We"," also"," discovered"," that"," the"," interaction"," between"," plasma"," flows"," and"," magnetic"," fields"," plays"," a"," significant"," role"," in"," the"," re","connection"," process","."," We"," further"," demonstrated"," that"," the"," efficiency"," of"," magnetic"," re","connection"," is"," proportional"," to"," the"," magnetic"," field"," strength"," and"," the"," plasma"," flow"," velocity","."," These"," findings"," have"," significant"," implications"," for"," understanding"," the"," dynamics"," of"," plasma"," systems"," in"," a"," variety"," of"," astro","physical"," and"," space"," environments","."," Our"," work"," contributes"," significantly"," to"," the"," ongoing"," efforts"," in"," developing"," a"," comprehensive"," theory"," of"," magnetic"," re","connection"," in"," high","-","energy"," plas","mas","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}